{"tid":2374024,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湯家驊：英國干預香港法治","createTime":"2021-01-21T02:21:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T07:10:42.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d9409e3592a4f89f2fb2e1ff524260f9c35f9843","tid":2374024,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T02:21:01.000Z","msg":"Now新聞台】李柱銘、黎智英等人涉嫌非法集結案，律政司改聘主控官，稱原本獲聘的英國御用大律師David Perry受英國社會壓力，資深大律師、行政會議成員湯家驊批評英國干預香港法治，但相信本地大律師可應付案件。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊：「非法集結案不是很艱難，可能是涉及知名度較高的人，但那又如何呢，都是面對同等的法律對待，看不到為何需要大費周章去英國找頂級資深大狀。英國出這些政治手段，暗地裡不多不少有些向香港法官施壓，他認為英國律師不可打不道德的官司，即是香港檢控是不道德，如果是檢控不道德，即要法官放人。」"},{"pid":"baaac694e1756123999eeae3f6efd4d24908d7c8","tid":2374024,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T02:21:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=421105\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D421105&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=6bf04d0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D421105&h=e077457d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=421105</a>"},{"pid":"4f151048009a7b785593a2478415c2ad88727ab6","tid":2374024,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T02:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a27af027fff324d9d84c1f6aa0a9b803aaafda1","tid":2374024,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T02:24:30.000Z","msg":"練好口才喺Hardtalk夠同主持fight先再講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55caab8086d6a485856455cb90afb7a85e073e1b","tid":2374024,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T02:24:39.000Z","msg":"點干預<br />\n派兵過黎?<br />\n平時講到咁無堅不摧<br />\n宜家英國講幾句就話震驚?"}